<p><b>
Welcome to ECS.
</b>
In the 2004 Times League Tables for University Departments, 
we were ranked first in the UK for
Electronics and Electrical Engineering and third in the UK for Computer Science.
We achieved 5* 
<a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20040415064220/http://www.rae.ac.uk"><acronym title="Research Assessment Exercise">RAE</acronym></a> research ratings in both areas and 
our research and teaching covers almost all aspects of these disciplines. 

In teaching we have been awarded the highest grades possible by the 
<a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20040415064220/http://www.qaa.ac.uk">
<acronym title="Quality Assurance Agency for Higher Education">QAA</acronym></a>. 
</p>
<p>
For queries concerning ECS enrolment and registration, The ECS Student Adminstrative Services telephone number is <nobr><b>+44 (0)23 8059 2900</b></nobr></p><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
